Class DefinitionsElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • jp.go.aist.six.oval.model.Element

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    DefinitionsComponent, DefinitionType

    public abstract class DefinitionsElement
extends Element
implements jp.go.aist.six.util.persist.Persistable<String>
    An OVAL definitions element. The kinds are definition, test, state, object, and variable. Every definitions element is identified by a pair of its identifier and version.
